One Direction Announced Their Made In The A.M. Tracklist, And We’re Kind Of Freaking Out 
Published By: MTV - Today 
Harry, Liam, Louis and Niall shared the song titles for their upcoming fifth album, Made In The A.M., on Snapchat Saturday afternoon....
